            , were indicted for that <rs id="t18151206-48-off265" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18151206-48-off265" type="offenceCategory" value="royalOffences"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18151206-48-off265" type="offenceSubcategory" value="coiningOffences"></interp>
