                  </persName>
            . I am a teller of the Bank. I look at the four dollars taken from the elder Bagnell's hand, they are counterfeit. The impressions on them are as stated in the indictment. I now look at the six found on the younger Bagnell they are all counterfeit, and bear similar impressions. I know look at the dyes, and think that those dollars were struck by them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18151206-48-person492">
                  JOSEPH 
                  HENRY HARPER
               <interp inst="t18151206-48-person492" type="surname" value="HENRY HARPER"></interp>
